freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: I developed severe dry eye and episcleritis on the 4th day after my vaccine.  This was never a problem I've had before.  It occurred in my left eye.  I missed 4 scheduled work days and had several doctor visits.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: After my first dose I developed an eye problem.  I am still having eye issues.  I followed up with my doctor today and I was diagnosed with nodular degeneration.  Not sure if this has anything to do with the vaccine but there is no identified etiology.
